        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Male genitalia: Typical structure of male genitalia of Cardiodactylus (species group Novaeguineae) in dorsal (A), ventral (B) and lateral (C) views, showing the terminology used in the descriptions below. Terminology used by TR is mentioned first and terminology by AG is mentioned in brackets. Abbreviations, see section Material and methods." ;
